# A TREND IN DIFFERENT STATES REGARDING "RAPES" AND "AGGRAVATED ASSAULTS"
```{r}
ggplot(Regional_Data) + aes(x= Rapes, y=Aggravated.Assaults) + theme_bw() + geom_line () + facet_grid(~ Region)  
